name: Kat Katnipp #4 "Night Ride"
description: This time I wanted to translate my deep aesthetical feeling of a night ride, the memories from my trip to US when I had to spend long nights driving between states and listening to my favorite music. I'm curious which other deepest corners of my soul I can express through the "Kat Katnipp" series. Now available only at HIC ET NUNC.
